  "body": "## Summary\n\nThis PR introduces **Iteration v4: Visual Analytics**. It replaces the static numbers with interactive charts to help users visualize their spending habits.\n\n### Changes\n- Installed `chart.js` and `react-chartjs-2`.\n- Integrated a **Doughnut/Pie Chart** for category-wise expense breakdown.\n- Integrated a **Bar Chart** to compare spending magnitude across categories.\n- Refactored `Dashboard.tsx` to use `useMemo` for efficient data aggregation.\n\n### Testing\n- Verified local build and chart rendering.\n- Ensured responsiveness across screen sizes.",
